{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"<input type=\"checkbox\">","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Input/checkbox","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>HTML input 元素&nbsp;<strong><code>&lt;input type=\"checkbox\"&gt;</code></strong> 允许你为表单中（或不在表单中）的提交项选择一个单一值。</p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect1\">\n<p><strong>注意</strong>：&nbsp;若表单提交时，checkbox 未勾选，则提交的值并非为 value=unchecked；此时的值不会被提交到服务器。</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"属性","title":"属性","isH3":false,"content":"<p>该元素包含<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes\">全局属性</a>。</p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"checked\"><a id=\"attr-checked\" href=\"#attr-checked\"><b><code>checked</code></b></a></dt>\n <dd>\n <p>当<strong>type</strong>属性的值为<code>checkbox 时</code>, 这个属性的存在表示 input 是否默认被选中。你可以将该属性设置为<code>checked=\"checked\"，</code>或更简单地只设置为<code>checked。</code></p>\n </dd>\n <dt id=\"value\"><a id=\"attr-value\" href=\"#attr-value\"><b><code>value</code></b></a></dt>\n <dd>指定 input 的值。如果省略，获取该元素的值的结果为字符串\"on\"。<br>\n 请注意，如果 value 值发生改变后页面重新加载，Gecko 和 IE<a href=\"https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=46845#c186\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">会忽略 HTML 源代码中设置的 value 值</a>。</dd>\n <dt id=\"indeterminate\"><a id=\"attr-indeterminate\" href=\"#attr-indeterminate\"><b><code>indeterminate</code></b></a></dt>\n <dd>指定 checkbox 处于不定状态（在大多数平台，这样会产生一个划过 checkbox 的横线）。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>input</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>checkbox<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>cbox1<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">value</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>first_checkbox<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>label</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">for</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>cbox1<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>This is the first checkbox<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>label</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>input</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>checkbox<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>cbox2<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">value</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>second_checkbox<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">checked</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>checked<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>label</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">for</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>cbox2<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>This is the second checkbox, which is checked<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>label</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<p>以上代码将产生 2 个 checkbox，如下所示：</p>\n\n<p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"Example sample\" id=\"frame_example\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Input/checkbox/_sample_.example.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"规范","title":"规范","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td>规范</td>\n   <td>状态</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/forms.html#checkbox-state-(type=checkbox)\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">&lt;checkbox&gt;</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Living Standard</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html52/forms.html#checkbox-state-(type=checkbox)\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">&lt;checkbox&gt;</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recommendation</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html401/interact/forms.html#checkbox\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML 4.01 Specification<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">&lt;checkbox&gt;</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recommendation</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"html.elements.input.input-checkbox","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Input/checkbox/bcd.json"}}],"toc":[{"text":"属性","id":"属性"},{"text":"示例","id":"example"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"}],"summary":"HTML input 元素 <input type=\"checkbox\"> 允许你为表单中（或不在表单中）的提交项选择一个单一值。","popularity":0.0032,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"<input type=\"checkbox\">","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"<input type=\"checkbox\">","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"<input type=\"checkbox\">","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"<input type=\"checkbox\">","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"<input type=\"checkbox\">","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"<input type=\"checkbox\">","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/html/element/input/checkbox","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web